ESP32-CAM DEEP SLEEP TIME LAPSE CAMERA  PROOF-OF-CONCEPT
PICTURE STORED IN SD CARD AND THEN UPLOADED VIA WIFI
TO A SERVER USING HTTP MULTIPART POST
